description: Up your Friday night dinner with this chicken sausage roll recipe from Clarissa in WA. The whole family will love these crispy, veggie-packed pastries.
name: Chicken & Veg Sausage Rolls Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Whisk egg and milk in a small bowl. Brush sausage rolls with egg mixture. Bake for 30 minutes or until golden and cooked through. Serve with sauce.
